So, given the code:

```
class Thing {

private Baz baz;
private String s;

Foo doStuff(Bar bar) {
   // what goes here
}
```

I’d want to synthesize:

```
    Foo doStuff(Bar bar) {
          Frob frob = new Frob(s);
          return new Foo(bar, baz, frob);
    } 
